### Login
POST http://localhost:5150/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "operator",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Config
GET http://localhost:5150/config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Config
PUT http://localhost:5150/config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tempMax": 75,
  "humidityMax": 60
}

### Get Alerts (all open)
GET http://localhost:5150/alerts?status=open
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Alerts (acknowledged, with date range)
GET http://localhost:5150/alerts?status=ack&from=2025-10-01T00:00:00Z&to=2025-10-07T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Acknowledge Alert
POST http://localhost:5150/alerts/{{alertId}}/ack
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
